<p>Given a sorted array, find the index of an element using a binary search algorithm.</p>

<h3 id="풀이">풀이</h3>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kd">var</span> <span class="nx">binarySearch</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="kd">function</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">array</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">target</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
